title: [Boreas Hills, Etesian Terrace]
description: Tidy cottages and homes line the road, each with a small garden in front.  Various birch trees dot the ground around and behind the cottages, while a wooden gate leads through a stone wall behind a line of magnolias.

Tidy cottages and homes line the road, their lit windows illuminating the small garden in front of each.  Various birch trees dot the ground around and behind the cottages, while a wooden gate with a lantern on each side leads through a stone wall behind a line of magnolias.
